name: Workout
description:
Workout like never before! 
 Join us for the greatest workout of the year. We start easy and accessible and then we ramp it up towards the end. You join and keep up for as long as you can. Our goal is for everyone to be able to at the end of the day feel good about themselves.

name: Dinner
description: Tired of living life alone during the crisis? Come eat at our amazing resturant 'Great FKN Food'. We've taken all the precations necessary for you and our other guests to enjoy a corona friendly experience with food, drink and entertainment.

name: Hangout
description: We know times are hard during the pendemic hopefully our online hangout can give you some long awaited social interraction. Join us over a glas of wine or just as we talk about interesting subjects. Expand your friend list and once you connect you can keep up the conversations on your own!
